.widget.statistics
  .widget__header
    h2.widget__header__title Statistics
      span.widget__header__subtitle (do you read or just save?)
    .widget__header__action
      a.icon((click)="prevMonth()")
        i.fas.fa-chevron-left
      span.mx-2 {{monthNames[(month$ | async) - 1]}} {{year$ | async}}
      a.icon(*ngIf="doesNextMonthExist$ | async", (click)="nextMonth()")
        i.fas.fa-chevron-right
  .widget__body.px-0
    tt-dashboard-statistics([statistics]="statistics$ | async")
  .widget__info(*ngIf="!(statistics$ | async)") No statistics for this period yet... What about to read something?
